<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="logo.png">
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes" />
    <title> MEN </title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Cairo:wght@300;400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <style>
        /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: #060812;
            color: #f0f4ff;
            font-family: 'Cairo', 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #060812;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #021ca4, #1a3a9e);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 92%;
            max-width: 1360px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 18px;
        }

        :root {
            --blue-deep: #021ca4;
            --blue-mid: #1a3a9e;
            --blue-light: #4a7aff;
            --blue-glow: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.35);
            --blue-soft: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            --silver: #e8ecf4;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --card-bg: rgba(10, 16, 32, 0.72);
            --card-border: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.20);
            --shadow-blue: 0 8px 40px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
            --transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
            --radius-xl: 28px;
            --radius-2xl: 42px;
        }

        .bg-ambient {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -2;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 30%, rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10) 0%, transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 70%, rgba(26, 58, 158, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, #060812 0%, #030510 100%);
        }
        .bg-ambient::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='80' height='80' viewBox='0 0 80 80' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23021ca4' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M50 40v-4h-4v4h-8v4h8v8h4v-8h8v-4h-8zm0-30V6h-4v4h-8v4h8v8h4v-8h8V10h-8zM10 40v-4H6v4H-2v4h8v8h4v-8h8v-4h-8zm0-30V6H6v4H-2v4h8v8h4v-8h8V10h-8z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        h1,
        h2,
        h3,
        h4 {
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
        }
        h3 {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
        }

        .section-label {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .section-label .line {
            flex: 1;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue-deep), transparent);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        .section-label h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, var(--blue-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            white-space: nowrap;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .section-label .icon-badge {
            background: var(--blue-soft);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        /* ===== BUTTONS ===== */
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 38px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 60px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.5);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.25);
            color: #f0f4ff;
            padding: 14px 38px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 60px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
            border-color: var(--blue-light);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
        }
        .btn-outline-blue {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--blue-deep);
            color: var(--blue-light);
            padding: 8px 26px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-outline-blue:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .btn-cart {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-cart:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.4);
        }
        .btn-cart-remove {
            background: rgba(200, 50, 50, 0.10);
            border: 1px solid rgba(200, 50, 50, 0.2);
            color: #ff7a7a;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
        .btn-cart-remove:hover {
            background: #cc4444;
            color: white;
            border-color: #cc4444;
        }
        .btn-ai-search {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .btn-ai-search:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .btn-pass {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5b342, #e8912e);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            color: #060812;
            font-weight: 800;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-pass:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.4);
        }
        .btn-pass-sm {
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        /* ===== HEADER ===== */
        header {
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.88);
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        header.scrolled {
            background: rgba(4, 6, 14, 0.96);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 52px;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .logo:hover img {
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1) drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.3));
        }
        .logo h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 40%, var(--blue-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .header-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .login-header-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 10px 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.2);
        }
        .login-header-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 36px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.4);
        }
        .menu-toggle-btn {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .menu-toggle-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            transform: rotate(90deg);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
        }
        .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute;
            top: 80px;
            left: auto;
            right: 20px;
            background: rgba(8, 10, 22, 0.96);
            backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
            min-width: 220px;
            padding: 10px 0;
            z-index: 1100;
            transform: scale(0.92) translateY(-8px);
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .dropdown-menu.show {
            transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }
        .dropdown-menu a {
            display: block;
            padding: 12px 26px;
            color: #c0c8e8;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: 0.25s;
            border-right: 3px solid transparent;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }
        .dropdown-menu a i {
            margin-left: 14px;
            width: 24px;
            color: var(--blue-deep);
            opacity: 0.5;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .dropdown-menu a:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border-right-color: var(--blue-deep);
            padding-right: 32px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .dropdown-menu a.active-drop {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            border-right-color: var(--blue-deep);
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }
        .dropdown-menu a.active-drop i {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* ===== PAGES ===== */
        .page {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeRise 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }
        .page.active {
            display: block;
        }
        @keyframes fadeRise {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.98);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
            }
        }

        /* ===== HERO ===== */
        .hero-luxury {
            padding: 100px 20px 70px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08), transparent 70%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
        }
        .hero-luxury .orb {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.25;
        }
        .hero-luxury .orb.orb-1 {
            width: 450px;
            height: 450px;
            top: -25%;
            left: -15%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.2), transparent 70%);
            animation: orbFloat 22s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        .hero-luxury .orb.orb-2 {
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            bottom: -25%;
            right: -15%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26, 58, 158, 0.15), transparent 70%);
            animation: orbFloat 26s ease-in-out infinite alternate-reverse;
        }
        @keyframes orbFloat {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.15);
            }
        }
        .hero-luxury .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            padding: 6px 24px 6px 20px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .hero-luxury .badge i {
            color: var(--blue-deep);
        }
        .hero-luxury h2 {
            font-size: 4.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.05;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 20%, var(--blue-light) 60%, #021ca4 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
        }
        .hero-luxury h2 .highlight {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5b342, #e8912e);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #f5b342;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .hero-luxury p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #a0b0d4;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 34px;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            line-height: 1.9;
        }
        .hero-luxury .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 18px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* ===== GAMES GRID ===== */
        .games-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 28px;
            margin: 30px 0 50px;
        }
        .game-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .game-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.01);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
        }
        .game-card .game-img {
            height: 200px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        .game-card .game-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s ease;
        }
        .game-card:hover .game-img img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }
        .game-card .game-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 14px;
            right: 14px;
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .game-card .game-badge.premium {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5b342, #e8912e);
            color: #060812;
        }
        .game-card .game-content {
            padding: 22px 24px 24px;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .game-card .game-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .game-card .game-content .game-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 18px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #8890b0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .game-card .game-content .game-meta i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-left: 4px;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        .game-card .game-content p {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .game-card .game-content .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        /* ===== FEATURED BANNER ===== */
        .featured-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06), rgba(10, 16, 32, 0.6));
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            padding: 40px 48px;
            margin: 30px 0 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }
        .featured-banner::after {
            content: '✦';
            position: absolute;
            top: -20%;
            right: -5%;
            font-size: 12rem;
            color: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .featured-banner .text h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .featured-banner .text h2 i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .featured-banner .text p {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        /* ===== STATS ===== */
        .stats-showcase {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px 70px;
            padding: 44px 30px;
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            margin: 50px 0;
        }
        .stats-showcase .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stats-showcase .stat-item .number {
            font-size: 3.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, var(--blue-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .stats-showcase .stat-item .label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #8890b0;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* ===== NEWS LUXURY ===== */
        .news-luxury-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 28px;
            margin: 30px 0 50px;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: stretch;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 56px -16px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-img {
            flex: 1 1 280px;
            height: 260px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.6s;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main:hover .tile-img img {
            transform: scale(1.04);
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-content {
            flex: 2 1 300px;
            padding: 30px 38px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-content p {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            margin: 8px 0 16px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -12px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub .tile-img {
            height: 180px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub .tile-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub:hover .tile-img img {
            transform: scale(1.06);
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub .tile-content {
            padding: 20px 24px 24px;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub .tile-content h4 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .news-luxury-grid .tile-sub .tile-content p {
            color: #a0a8c0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin: 4px 0 12px;
        }

        /* ===== STORE ===== */
        .store-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06), rgba(10, 16, 32, 0.5));
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            padding: 32px 44px;
            margin: 20px 0 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 18px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }
        .store-banner h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .store-banner h2 i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .store-banner p {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }
        .search-cart-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .cart-ai-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .cart-toggle-btn {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .cart-toggle-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .cart-badge {
            background: var(--blue-deep);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 1px 8px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            min-width: 22px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .btn-ai-assistant {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
        }
        .btn-ai-assistant:hover {
            transform: scale(1.04) translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 36px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.3);
        }
        .search-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .search-wrapper input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 24px 14px 60px;
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.7);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            border-radius: 60px;
            color: #f0f4ff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }
        .search-wrapper input:focus {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.85);
        }
        .search-wrapper input::placeholder {
            color: #5a607a;
        }
        .search-wrapper .search-icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 22px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--blue-deep);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.4;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .shop-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .product-item {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 380px;
        }
        .product-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 56px -16px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
        }
        .product-item.pass-item {
            border-color: #f5b342;
            background: rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.04);
        }
        .product-item.pass-item:hover {
            border-color: #e8912e;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 56px -16px rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.12);
        }
        .product-item.pass-item .product-name {
            color: #f5b342;
        }
        .product-item.pass-item .product-price {
            color: #f5b342;
        }
        .product-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s;
            background: #0a0a14;
        }
        .product-item:hover .product-img {
            transform: scale(1.04);
        }
        .product-info {
            padding: 18px 20px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .product-name {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #f0f4ff;
        }
        .product-price {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            margin: 4px 0 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
        }
        .product-price .currency-icon,
        .price .currency-icon {
            height: 2.2rem;
            width: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06));
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .product-actions {
            margin-top: auto;
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .product-actions .btn-cart {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .product-actions .btn-ai-search {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .product-actions .btn-pass-sm {
            flex: 1;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        /* ===== PASS BANNER ===== */
        .pass-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.06), rgba(232, 145, 46, 0.10));
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.15);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            padding: 36px 44px;
            margin: 20px 0 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 24px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }
        .pass-banner::before {
            content: '✦';
            position: absolute;
            top: -30%;
            right: -5%;
            font-size: 14rem;
            color: rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.03);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .pass-banner .pass-text h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #f5b342;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .pass-banner .pass-text h2 i {
            margin-left: 12px;
        }
        .pass-banner .pass-text p {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .pass-banner .pass-features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px 28px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .pass-banner .pass-features .feat {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #d0d8ee;
        }
        .pass-banner .pass-features .feat i {
            color: #f5b342;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* ===== AI CHAT ===== */
        .ai-chat-box {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 14px;
            padding: 16px 14px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            max-height: 340px;
            min-height: 260px;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        .ai-message {
            max-width: 88%;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10);
        }
        .ai-message.user {
            align-self: flex-end;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 6px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .ai-message.bot {
            align-self: flex-start;
            background: rgba(10, 12, 24, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            color: #d0d8ee;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 6px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;
            max-width: 92%;
        }
        .ai-message.bot strong,
        .ai-message.bot b {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .ai-message.bot .pass-highlight {
            color: #f5b342;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        .ai-message.bot ul,
        .ai-message.bot ol {
            padding-right: 24px;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .ai-message.bot li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .ai-message.bot table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .ai-message.bot th,
        .ai-message.bot td {
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            text-align: right;
        }
        .ai-message.bot th {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .ai-message.bot tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .ai-message.thinking {
            align-self: flex-start;
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            border: 1px dashed rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
            color: var(--blue-light);
            border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 10px 18px;
        }
        .ai-message.thinking .spinner {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 3px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border-top: 3px solid var(--blue-deep);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            0% {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        .ai-product-card {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
        }
        .ai-product-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }
        .ai-product-card img {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 14px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
        }
        .ai-product-card .info {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 3px;
        }
        .ai-product-card .info .name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .ai-product-card .info .price {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .ai-product-card .btn-add-from-chat {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
        }
        .ai-product-card .btn-add-from-chat:hover {
            transform: scale(1.06);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.2);
        }

        .ai-quick-btns {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .ai-quick-btns .qbtn {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        }
        .ai-quick-btns .qbtn:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            border-color: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .ai-quick-btns .qbtn i {
            margin-left: 6px;
            color: var(--blue-deep);
        }
        .ai-quick-btns .qbtn.pass-btn {
            background: rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.06);
            border-color: rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.10);
            color: #f5b342;
        }
        .ai-quick-btns .qbtn.pass-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.12);
            border-color: rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.20);
        }
        .ai-quick-btns .qbtn.pass-btn i {
            color: #f5b342;
        }

        .ai-input-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .ai-input-row input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 22px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            color: #f0f4ff;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .ai-input-row input:focus {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .ai-input-row input::placeholder {
            color: #4a5070;
        }
        .ai-input-row button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 0 28px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
        }
        .ai-input-row button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.04);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
        }

        .ai-modal {
            background: rgba(8, 10, 20, 0.96);
            backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 520px;
            height: 580px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 24px 28px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }
        .ai-modal h3 {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .ai-modal h3 i {
            color: var(--blue-deep);
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
        .ai-modal .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 18px;
            left: 22px;
            font-size: 26px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #5a607a;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .ai-modal .modal-close:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: rotate(90deg) scale(1.1);
        }
        .ai-modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            z-index: 3500;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .ai-modal-overlay.active {
            display: flex;
        }

        /* ===== CART MODAL ===== */
        .cart-modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            z-index: 3000;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .cart-modal-overlay.active {
            display: flex;
        }
        .cart-modal {
            background: rgba(8, 10, 20, 0.96);
            backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 520px;
            padding: 36px 32px;
            position: relative;
            max-height: 90vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }
        .cart-modal .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 16px;
            left: 22px;
            font-size: 26px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #5a607a;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .cart-modal .modal-close:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }
        .cart-modal h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cart-modal h3 i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .cart-items-list {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            max-height: 300px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .cart-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .cart-item img {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        .cart-item .item-details {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        .cart-item .item-details .name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .cart-item .qty-control {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
        .qty-btn {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            color: var(--blue-light);
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .qty-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .qty-number {
            font-weight: 700;
            min-width: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .cart-item .item-total {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .cart-total-display {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            border-top: 2px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            padding-top: 14px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .cart-total-display .total-price {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .discount-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .discount-row input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            color: #f0f4ff;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .discount-row input:focus {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.02);
        }
        .discount-row .btn-apply {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .discount-row .btn-apply:hover {
            transform: scale(1.04);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
        }
        .discount-msg {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #4caf50;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .discount-msg.error {
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        .cart-modal .input-field {
            margin: 18px 0;
        }
        .cart-modal .input-field label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .cart-modal .input-field input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            border-radius: 60px;
            color: #f0f4ff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .cart-modal .input-field input:focus {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.02);
        }
        .cart-modal .btn-submit {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
        }
        .cart-modal .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
        }
        .cart-empty {
            text-align: center;
            color: #5a607a;
            padding: 24px 0;
        }

        /* ===== REVIEWS ===== */
        .reviews-section {
            margin: 60px 0 30px;
        }
        .reviews-carousel-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        .reviews-carousel {
            overflow: hidden;
            flex: 1;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        }
        .reviews-track {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            will-change: transform;
        }
        .review-card {
            min-width: 280px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 26px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .review-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -12px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .review-stars {
            color: #f5b342;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        .review-text {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #d0d8ee;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .review-author {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }
        .carousel-btn {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            color: var(--blue-light);
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .carousel-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .carousel-btn:disabled {
            opacity: 0.15;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* ===== ABOUT ===== */
        .about-stats {
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            padding: 50px 30px;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }
        .about-stats h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, var(--blue-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .stats-flex {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .stat-item .number {
            font-size: 3.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, var(--blue-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .stat-item .label {
            color: #8890b0;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* ===== EXTRA SECTIONS ===== */
        .timeline-section {
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 24px 28px;
            flex: 1 1 200px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .timeline-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
        }
        .timeline-item .year {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }
        .timeline-item .desc {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .team-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 24px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .team-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
        }
        .team-card img {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 3px solid var(--blue-deep);
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .team-card .info {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .team-card h4 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .team-card p {
            color: #8890b0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .faq-section {
            margin: 50px 0;
        }
        .faq-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        .faq-item {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 20px 24px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .faq-item:hover {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
        }
        .faq-item .q {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .faq-item .q i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .faq-item .a {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: none;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .faq-item.active .a {
            display: block;
        }
        .faq-item.active .q i {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
        }

        /* ===== PORTAL ===== */
        .portal-container .card-soft {
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            padding: 28px 32px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .soft-header {
            background: rgba(6, 8, 18, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 16px 28px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .soft-header .logo h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .soft-header .logo h2 i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .profile-avatar {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid var(--blue-deep);
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
        }
        .tabs-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            padding: 6px;
            border-radius: 80px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .tab-soft {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8890b0;
            border-radius: 60px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .tab-soft.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
        }
        .tab-soft:hover:not(.active) {
            color: #ffffff;
            background: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .tab-content {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeRise 0.4s ease;
        }
        .tab-content.active-content {
            display: block;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            padding: 12px 0;
        }
        .info-label {
            width: 160px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }
        .table-clean {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .table-clean th,
        .table-clean td {
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            text-align: right;
        }
        .table-clean th {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            padding: 22px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            flex: 1;
        }
        .stat-card h4 {
            color: #8890b0;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .stat-card div {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }

        .circular-progress {
            position: relative;
            width: 160px;
            height: 160px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .circular-bg {
            stroke: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            stroke-width: 8;
            fill: none;
        }
        .circular-fill {
            stroke: url(#blueGrad);
            stroke-width: 8;
            fill: none;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            transition: stroke-dashoffset 0.4s ease;
        }
        .progress-text {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .progress-days {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .progress-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #8890b0;
        }
        .detailed-timer {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            font-family: 'Outfit', monospace;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--blue-light);
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .deadline-info {
            color: #8890b0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .btn-task {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 10px 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 6px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .btn-task:hover {
            transform: scale(1.04);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.10);
        }
        .btn-task-expired {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6b3a3a, #a55a5a);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .btn-task-expired:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(165, 90, 90, 0.15);
        }

        /* ===== EMPLOYEE CARD ===== */
        .employee-card-luxury {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: rgba(8, 10, 20, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            padding: 26px 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            transition: var(--transition);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 28px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .employee-card-luxury::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -60%;
            left: -60%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03), transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .employee-card-luxury:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
        }
        .employee-card-luxury>* {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .card-avatar-lg {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.06);
            object-fit: cover;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .employee-card-luxury:hover .card-avatar-lg {
            border-color: var(--blue-light);
            box-shadow: 0 0 70px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
        }
        .card-info-center {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        .card-name {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .status-badge-lg {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(0, 200, 0, 0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 200, 0, 0.06);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 4px 18px 4px 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4caf50;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .status-badge-lg .dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #4caf50;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.10);
        }
        @keyframes pulse-dot {
            0% {
                opacity: 0.3;
                transform: scale(0.8);
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1.2);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 0.3;
                transform: scale(0.8);
            }
        }
        .card-details-grid-h {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4px 24px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 8px 0 10px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.02);
        }
        .card-details-grid-h .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #b0b8d0;
        }
        .card-details-grid-h .detail-item i {
            color: var(--blue-deep);
            width: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        .card-details-grid-h .detail-item .value {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .card-right-col {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .barcode-wrapper-h {
            width: 180px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .barcode-wrapper-h img {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .barcode-wrapper-h .scanner-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
            animation: scanMove 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        @keyframes scanMove {
            0% {
                top: 0;
                opacity: 0.1;
            }
            20% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            80% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                top: 100%;
                opacity: 0.1;
            }
        }
        .discipline-section-h {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 4px 0 2px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            border-radius: 28px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.02);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .discipline-item-h {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .discipline-item-h .number {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .discipline-item-h .label {
            color: #8890b0;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        .discipline-item-h.green .number {
            color: #4caf50;
        }
        .discipline-item-h.red .number {
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        .discipline-item-h.yellow .number {
            color: #f5b342;
        }
        .card-footer-text-h {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #4a5070;
            margin-top: 4px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.02);
            padding-top: 6px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .following-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .following-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .following-item:hover {
            border-color: rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }
        .following-item i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            width: 28px;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        .following-item .fname {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ===== MODAL LOGIN ===== */
        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(28px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px);
            z-index: 2000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            visibility: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }
        .modal-overlay.active {
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .modal-container {
            background: rgba(8, 10, 20, 0.96);
            backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 440px;
            padding: 40px 34px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .modal-container h3 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .modal-container h3 i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-left: 10px;
        }
        .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 18px;
            left: 22px;
            font-size: 26px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #5a607a;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .modal-close:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }
        .input-icon {
            position: relative;
            margin: 22px 0;
        }
        .input-icon i {
            position: absolute;
            right: 18px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--blue-deep);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        .input-icon input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 48px 14px 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            border-radius: 60px;
            color: #f0f4ff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .input-icon input:focus {
            border-color: var(--blue-deep);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.02);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-login-modal {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-deep), var(--blue-mid));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.08);
        }
        .btn-login-modal:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.12);
        }
        .login-error-msg {
            color: #ff6b6b;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .hidden {
            display: none;
        }

        /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
        footer {
            background: #04060e;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            padding: 50px 0 30px;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }
        .footer-flex {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .footer-col h4 {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .footer-col p {
            color: #6a708a;
            margin: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .footer-col p i {
            color: #a0b0d4;
            opacity: 0.7;
            width: 20px;
        }
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .social-icons a {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #6a708a;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .social-icons a:hover {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        .copyright {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.03);
            color: #4a5070;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .copyright span {
            color: var(--blue-light);
        }

        /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
        @media (max-width:1200px) {
            .shop-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
            .hero-luxury h2 {
                font-size: 3.2rem;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width:992px) {
            .shop-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }
            .news-luxury-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .news-luxury-grid .tile-main {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-img {
                height: 200px;
            }
            .hero-luxury h2 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
            .faq-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .employee-card-luxury {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .card-details-grid-h {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .card-right-col {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .barcode-wrapper-h {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 220px;
            }
            .pass-banner {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .pass-banner .pass-features {
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width:768px) {
            .header-content {
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .logo img {
                height: 40px;
            }
            .logo h1 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .login-header-btn {
                padding: 8px 18px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                gap: 6px;
            }
            .menu-toggle-btn {
                width: 42px;
                height: 42px;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .dropdown-menu {
                min-width: 190px;
                right: 10px;
                top: 70px;
            }
            .dropdown-menu a {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            .header-actions {
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .btn-primary,
            .btn-secondary {
                padding: 10px 24px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            .soft-header {
                padding: 12px 18px;
            }
            .tab-soft {
                padding: 6px 16px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
            .store-banner {
                padding: 24px 20px;
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 14px;
            }
            .store-banner h2 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
            .shop-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 16px;
            }
            .product-img {
                height: 170px;
            }
            .product-price {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
            .product-price .currency-icon {
                height: 1.8rem;
            }
            .review-card {
                min-width: 220px;
            }
            .carousel-btn {
                width: 36px;
                height: 36px;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .cart-ai-row {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
            .cart-toggle-btn,
            .btn-ai-assistant {
                flex: 1;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .ai-modal {
                height: 480px;
                padding: 16px 18px;
            }
            .ai-quick-btns .qbtn {
                font-size: 0.7rem;
                padding: 4px 14px;
            }
            .hero-luxury {
                padding: 60px 16px 50px;
                border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            }
            .hero-luxury h2 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            .hero-luxury p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .stats-showcase {
                gap: 30px 40px;
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .stats-showcase .stat-item .number {
                font-size: 2.6rem;
            }
            .featured-banner {
                padding: 28px 24px;
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .featured-banner .text h2 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
            .games-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .section-label h3 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-content h4 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .news-luxury-grid .tile-main .tile-content {
                padding: 20px 24px;
            }
            .about-stats {
                padding: 30px 16px;
            }
            .stats-flex {
                gap: 30px;
            }
            .stat-item .number {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
            .cart-modal {
                padding: 28px 20px;
            }
            .cart-modal h3 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .footer-flex {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 24px;
            }
            .timeline {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .timeline-item {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
            }
            .team-grid {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            .team-card {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .team-card .info {
                text-align: center;
            }
            .employee-card-luxury {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .card-name {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .card-avatar-lg {
                width: 80px;
                height: 80px;
            }
            .card-details-grid-h {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 4px 12px;
                padding: 10px 14px;
            }
            .discipline-section-h {
                gap: 12px;
            }
            .barcode-wrapper-h {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .pass-banner {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }
            .pass-banner .pass-text h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .pass-banner .pass-features .feat {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width:480px) {
            .login-header-btn {
                padding: 6px 14px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                gap: 4px;
            }
            .menu-toggle-btn {
                width: 38px;
                height: 38px;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .dropdown-menu {
                min-width: 170px;
                right: 5px;
                top: 62px;
            }
            .shop-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 12px;
            }
            .product-img {
                height: 130px;
            }
            .product-name {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
            .product-price {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            .product-price .currency-icon {
                height: 1.4rem;
            }
            .review-card {
                min-width: 170px;
                padding: 16px;
            }
            .ai-modal {
                height: 420px;
                padding: 12px 14px;
            }
            .ai-message {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                padding: 8px 14px;
            }
            .hero-luxury h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .hero-luxury .btn-primary,
            .hero-luxury .btn-secondary {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }
            .games-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .section-label h3 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .featured-banner .text h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            .store-banner h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            .modal-container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .modal-container h3 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .employee-card-luxury {
                padding: 16px;
                gap: 16px;
            }
            .card-name {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .card-avatar-lg {
                width: 64px;
                height: 64px;
            }
            .card-details-grid-h {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding: 8px 12px;
            }
            .discipline-section-h {
                gap: 8px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                padding: 6px 12px;
            }
            .discipline-item-h .number {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .soft-header .logo h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .profile-avatar {
                width: 70px;
                height: 70px;
            }
            .tabs-nav {
                gap: 4px;
                padding: 4px;
            }
            .tab-soft {
                padding: 4px 12px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
            }
            .info-label {
                width: 120px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }
            .team-grid {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            .barcode-wrapper-h {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .pass-banner .pass-text h2 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
            .pass-banner .pass-features .feat {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
            .pass-banner {
                padding: 18px 16px;
            }
        }

        /* ===== TOAST ===== */
        .toast-notification {
            position: fixed;
            top: 24px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: rgba(8, 10, 20, 0.92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.04);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            color: #f0f4ff;
            z-index: 9999;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            direction: rtl;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            animation: toastSlide 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }
        .toast-notification i {
            color: var(--blue-light);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .toast-notification i.pass-icon {
            color: #f5b342;
        }
        @keyframes toastSlide {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-20px) scale(0.95);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0) scale(1);
            }
        }

        /* ===== FIXED AD (hidden for subscribers) ===== */
        .fixed-ad {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            max-width: 180px;
            z-index: 9999;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 2px solid rgba(2, 28, 164, 0.15);
            background: #0a0a14;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        .fixed-ad:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .fixed-ad img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }
        .close-ad-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 6px;
            right: 8px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            width: 26px;
            height: 26px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .close-ad-btn:hover {
            background: #cc4444;
            transform: scale(1.15);
        }
        .close-ad-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }
        @media (max-width:480px) {
            .fixed-ad {
                max-width: 120px;
                bottom: 15px;
                right: 15px;
            }
            .close-ad-btn {
                width: 22px;
                height: 22px;
                font-size: 14px;
                top: 4px;
                right: 6px;
            }
        }

        /* ===== PASS POPUP ===== */
        .pass-popup-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(28px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(28px);
            z-index: 4000;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .pass-popup-overlay.active {
            display: flex;
        }
        .pass-popup {
            background: rgba(8, 10, 20, 0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(32px);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(245, 179, 66, 0.12);
            border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 480px;
            padding: 40px 34px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .pass-popup .popup-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 16px;
            left: 22px;
            font-size: 26px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #5a607a;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .pass-popup .popup-close:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }
        .pass-popup .popup-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #f5b342;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .pass-popup h2 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #f5b342;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .pass-popup p {
            color: #b0b8d0;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .pass-popup .popup-features {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            text-align: right;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            padding: 18px 24px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        }
        .pass-popup .popup-features .feat {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            color: #d0d8ee;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .pass-popup .popup-features .feat i {
            color: #f5b342;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .pass-popup .btn-pass {
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 16px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .pass-popup .btn-secondary {
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="bg-ambient"></div>

    <!-- ===== HEADER ===== -->
    <header id="mainHeader">
        <div class="container header-content">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="https://www.socialcreator.com/srv/imgs/ti_imgs/200176_309202.png" alt="MEN">
            </div>
            <div class="header-actions">
                <button id="headerLoginBtn" class="login-header-btn"><i class="fas fa-fingerprint"></i> تسجيل دخول </button>
                <button id="menuToggleBtn" class="menu-toggle-btn"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-vertical"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div id="dropdownMenu" class="dropdown-menu">
                <a data-page="home"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> الرئيسية</a>
                <a data-page="news"><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> الألعاب</a>
                <a data-page="store"><i class="fas fa-store"></i> المتجر</a>
                <a data-page="about"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> من نحن</a>
                <a data-page="timeline"><i class="fas fa-timeline"></i> رحلتنا</a>
                <a data-page="team"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> الفريق</a>
                <a data-page="faq"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> الأسئلة</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">

            <!-- ===== HOME ===== -->
            <section id="home" class="page active">

                <!-- ===== PASS BANNER ON VISIT (رسالة في الزيارة) ===== -->
                <div class="pass-banner" id="passBanner">
                    <div class="pass-text">
                        <h2><i class="fas fa-crown"></i> اشتراك MEN Pass</h2>
                        <p>افتح عالم الألعاب والمحتوى الحصري مع اشتراك MEN Pass. استمتع بتجربة لا مثيل لها.</p>
                        <div class="pass-features">
                            <span class="feat"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> ألعاب أكثر</span>
                            <span class="feat"><i class="fas fa-video"></i> فيديوهات حصرية للمشتركين</span>
                            <span class="feat"><i class="fas fa-flask"></i> بحوث متقدمة</span>
                            <span class="feat"><i class="fas fa-ban"></i> بدون إعلانات</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <button class="btn-pass" id="passBannerBtn"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i> اشترك الآن</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- ===== الإعلان الثابت (يُخفى للمشتركين) ===== -->
                <div class="fixed-ad" id="fixedAd">
                    <button class="close-ad-btn" id="closeAdBtn" aria-label="إغلاق الإعلان">✕</button>
                    <img src="https://www.socialcreator.com/srv/imgs/ti_imgs/200764_328971.png" alt="إعلان">
                </div>

                <div class="hero-luxury">
                    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
                    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
                    <div class="badge"><i class="fas fa-"></i> Team · MEN</div>
                    <h2>سيطرة <span class="highlight">أقوى</span></h2>
                    <p>فريق اللاعبين وصنّاع المحتوى.</p>
                    <div class="btn-group">
                        <a href="pass.html" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> اشترك الان
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://youtube.com/@clan_men?si=8TEv8fKu5Coppwas" class="btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i> شاهد الفيديو</a>
                        <button class="btn-pass" id="heroPassBtn"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i> MEN Pass</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- NEWS -->
                <div class="section-label">
                    <span class="icon-badge"><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> أخبار</span>
                    <h3>أحدث الأخبار</h3>
                    <span class="line"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="news-luxury-grid">
                    <div class="tile-main">
                        <div class="tile-img"><img src="https://www.socialcreator.com/srv/imgs/ti_imgs/200685_328971.png" alt="Festival"></div>
                        <div class="tile-content">
                            <h4>فعالية سنوية</h4>
                            <p>حدث سنوي يجمع نخبة المبدعين في عالم الألعاب والمحتوى الرقمي.</p>
                            <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/festival-of-creativity/festival-of-creativity" class="btn-outline-blue"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> تفاصيل الحدث</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tile-sub">
                        <div class="tile-img"><img src="https://img.youm7.com/large/202312051043414341.jpg" alt="GTA"></div>
                        <div class="tile-content"><h4>GTA VI</h4><p>عالم مفتوح أسطوري ينتظرك.</p><a href="#" class="btn-outline-blue">استكشف</a></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tile-sub">
                        <div class="tile-img"><img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSUjzc13vNlX6UtyALKsXvpeEQor5f802tBiQ&s" alt="EA FC"></div>
                        <div class="tile-content"><h4>EA FC 26</h4><p>تطويرات ثورية في أسلوب اللعب.</p><a href="#" class="btn-outline-blue">استكشف</a></div>
